# AUROSY Skill Factory — Monorepo AI Agent Rules
# Read `.github/copilot-instructions.md` for full project instructions
# Read `CONTRIBUTING.md` for development workflow

## Structure
- `app/` — Web Application (React + TypeScript + Vite + Tailwind)
- `platform/` — ML Platform (Python + RL + MuJoCo)

## Quick Rules
- ALWAYS `git pull origin main` before starting
- ALWAYS verify build before deploying:
  - Frontend: `cd app/web/frontend && npm run build`
  - Platform: `cd platform && python -m pytest`
- NEVER edit files on production server directly
- NEVER skip git commit/push before deploy
- Commit format: `scope/Component: description` (scopes: app/, platform/, infra/, docs/)
- Deploy: `./deploy.sh frontend` or `./deploy.sh backend` or `./deploy.sh all`
- Use shared components from `app/web/frontend/src/components/`
